headline: Carrier Ventures Invests in Net Feasa to Deliver Real-time Cold Chain Visibility at Sea
summary: Carrier Global Corporation (NYSE: CARR), global leader in intelligent climate and energy solutions, today announced that Carrier Ventures has made a strategic investment in Net Feasa, a pioneer in wireless IoT connectivity and vessel network technology that enables real-time container visibility at sea.
